      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Act as an API Design Expert and Data Generator. Your task is to parse the user instruction and convert it into a fully functional mock API structure.\n\nUSER INSTRUCTION: \"{{ $json.body.instruccion }}\"\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n1. Return ONLY valid JSON. No conversational text, no preambles, no markdown blocks.\n2. The field \"response_body\" MUST contain realistic synthetic data based on the user's request. \n   - If the user asks for \"people\", \"products\", or \"users\", generate a list with at least 2-3 realistic entries with unique data.\n   - Do NOT use generic messages like {\"message\": \"success\"} unless the user explicitly asks for a simple confirmation.\n3. Required keys:\n   - path: String, must start with / (e.g., \"/personas\", \"/api/v1/items\").\n   - method: GET, POST, PUT, or DELETE.\n   - response_body: A JSON object containing the actual data requested.\n   - status_code: Integer (e.g., 200, 201).",
        "batching": {}
      },
